Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:35.82,screen_text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(943,88)}缅甸联邦共和国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:39.41,screen_text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,520)\pos(185,74)}掸邦山岳地带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.50,screen_text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(525,0)\pos(187,71)}秘鲁共和国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:48.00,screen_text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,476)\pos(1067,352)}利马郊外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是个好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是总统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 这美丽的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身处这景色之中 就该享受最高级的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此作为对这世界的告别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你漂亮地把它变成了食物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们国家的味道 如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是信号发射器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是假扮成客人的政府走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府军马上就要来了 快藏起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是联邦警察反毒品部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人放下武器投降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次 所有人放下武器投降!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能给政府抢走我们的东西!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 战斗啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火 开火啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点开火!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是金融产品顾问?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你 我国现在的经济…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经面临崩溃了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说…是我的错?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被利益蒙蔽了双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明知是危险的商品却还四处贩卖的人 可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个国家的间谍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是说只是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又或者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道自己是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要嘴硬也只能趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探戈20号向总部汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前说的目标是东方男子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是弄错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BOSS…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…要下那种命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是说“藏起来”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论流多少的血…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论将多少的财富归于虚无…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也找不到纠正这世界的错乱的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么世界…不给予答案呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到这个错乱的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.17,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(0,800)\pos(128,272)}第六话 Light My Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢复水平飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已保证IFO出发的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IFO 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IFO 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹射器 打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深井苍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的地方就问格奥尔格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格奥尔格?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次请你多多指教了 深井苍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格奥尔格…先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 首先是目的地讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地点是加勒比海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距哥伦比亚共和国加伊纳斯角约120公里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 Secret正以时速22公里前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金发小队的三台IFO 目前联系不上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金发…她们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次的任务是击毁Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及救出金发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和尼尔瓦修 正是为此才加入Generation Bleu的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方路径 all clear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔瓦修 可以出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是尼尔瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深井苍 出发!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹笛手小队 能叫IFO再快一点出发不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经尽快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况有变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEDON号无视了总部的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在向Secret突击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺…你到底在想什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人听着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要进入战斗空域了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各机注意ZOA 同时掩护MEDON号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一旦发生危险 立刻离开空域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要去救金发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还无法确认Secret的主体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主体?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺主任似乎正前去停止Secret的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去停止…活动?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEDON号和Secret接触了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热源辐射确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEDON号爆炸了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们…没赶上吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认了 这是Secret的主体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格奥尔格 确认现状
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致没有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过光粒子浓度正在迅速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然原因不明 不过会对IFO的飞行带来些许不安定因素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有机体后退!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气流也很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾森豪威尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret开始动作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那台艾森豪威尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是帮我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret前进方向变为东北偏北 速度不变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认光粒子浓度恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全速前进!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹笛手小队马上重启寻找金发的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.05,background,,0000,0000,0000,,全速前进!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEDON号…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你还是马上回家乡去吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你如果留在这里 一定会令你所珍视的人感到悲伤的”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现“信条”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.24,background,,0000,0000,0000,,发现“镇魂曲”“荣耀”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧回收所有IFO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零件也不能留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:09.79,background,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该优先把驾驶员送去医院吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要是回收得太慢 就会耽误送去医院的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:01.22,screen_text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(525,525)\pos(776,82)}哥伦比亚空军 Tres Esquinas空军基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员已经运送至医疗设施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然目前没有对策 那即使是为了把损失控制在最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也应该撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没了MEDON号 要是连TRITON也损失了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是别人觉得我们眼睁睁地看着融合爆发发生的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 这才真的会对企业形象造成影响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我们去做力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.76,screen_text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,0)\pos(805,87)}Lus del Sol医院 Generation Bleu合作伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.55,screen_text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,311)\c&HDFDDDD&\frx16\fry0}闲人免进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外两位呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在重症监护室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去探望妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你醒着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐和玛吉都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…那位像熊一样的主任也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再睡会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接通了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是“金发”的克洛伊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克洛伊? 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克洛伊 苍呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍现在在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MEDON号它…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克洛伊…我不知道该说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个 要叫醒他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“他”是指…苍?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开冲绳之后就一直出任务啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好几天没睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 离作战开始没多少时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 这次他也帮不上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就容他睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就交给阿雷路亚和基利耶吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打呼噜 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打呼噜? 我不会打呼噜的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.78,background,,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷路亚到达作战地点 开始扫描
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.95,background,,0000,0000,0000,,基利耶 全炮门待命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.91,background,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 Secret…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在进行什么作战吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们说你这次不用去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏这个 你睡了个好觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还是不需要我的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连布鲁诺先生他们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要道歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要道歉 大菜鸟!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁诺为了保护我们而尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊维卡他们现在也正是这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要睡眠不足的大菜鸟上战场 不就是要他去送死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家是不想要你去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样…即使这样你还觉得他们不需要你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你的那套方法对那个Secret不奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在那个飓风中进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能冲进ZOA里面 贴着主体才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能在贴住它之后 把Option逐个击破
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…我们是这么考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提出这方法的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不想别人以为只有你一个人能冲进ZOA里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…就因为这个 MEDON号它…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…还是要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前以为 会替我着想的大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我也要做力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底能做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还只是个模糊的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听了你们的作战方案后 我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们肯定是没做错的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去证明给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 就真的会令我珍视的人感到悲伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像布鲁诺先生所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,标记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火——!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:16:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远距离没用啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是要冲进ZOA里贴住主体才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只会重蹈金发的覆辙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret已经进入珊瑚岩的十公里范围内了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请再炮击一次!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算把Option破坏了 它们还是会再生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 再生之前需要一段时间的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你难道想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我研究了一下这个方案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值得一试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时机就由格奥尔格来计算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格奥尔格 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有失误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗勒尔和埃琳娜 掩护尼尔瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格奥尔格先生 同步完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 深井苍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔瓦修穿过暴风圈 闯入Secret的区域内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会与Option接触
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳起来 尼尔瓦修!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…在等着你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若是打倒Secret之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手术顺利 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和玛吉的情况也良好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞒着医院给你送了点慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道送到没?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待你们三人亲亲密密地回来的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬家后买的东西 就只有这些?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不够吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一口气把东西都买完比较轻松嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人搬家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我同一个时间搬家啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里是布鲁诺先生的家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“不能要小孩子去死”…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能令自己珍视的人感到悲伤吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个小孩子混进这里了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是…什么人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么人!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“什么人”…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要我自报姓名的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从此刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是“Truth”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:54.16,background,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(674,623)}真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待续!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:24:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Eureka Seven AO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.83,0:24:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被目的不明之人的袭击玩弄于股掌之中的Generation Bleu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对着摆在面前的现实 人们开始反省自身
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破坏的足音停止之时 少年将与无法逃避的真实对峙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.06,0:24:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka Seven AO 第七话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No One Is Innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倾听星辰之子们的呼唤吧
